Zoho Corporation - Programming Test


1. Write a program to print the below pattern.

Input: 5

5 5 5 5 5
5 4 4 4 4
5 4 3 3 3
5 4 3 2 2
5 4 3 2 1


package zoho;

public class Program1 {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
	
		
		int rows = 5;

	    for (int i = 1; i <= rows; ++i) 
	    {
	      for (int j = 1; j <= rows; ++j) 
	      {
	        System.out.print(j + " ");
	      }
	      System.out.println();
	}

}
}
